                             </p>
                                                      <p>
                                              Vadim Sadkov, <em>Netherlandish, Flemish and Dutch Drawings of the XVI-XVIII Centuries, Belgian and Dutch Drawings of the XIX-XX Centuries</em>, ed. Charles Dumas, Foundation for Cultural Inventory (Amsterdam, 2010), under cat. no. 232, p. 156
                             </p>
                                                      <p>
                                              William W. Robinson and Susan Anderson, <em>Drawings from the Age of Bruegel, Rubens, and Rembrandt: Highlights from the Collection of the Harvard Art Museums</em>, Harvard Art Museums (Cambridge, MA, 2016), p. 15, 23; cat. no. 50, pp. 176-178, repr. p. 177
                             </p>
